item.description: Cisco continues its strategy to merge the whole Campus Switch platform to a single Image, the newest step in this process is IOS XE 16.1.1. Currently only available for the Cat3k Platform (3650, 3850) but releases for the other Catalyst platforms should follow. In this post i show you how to upgrade your Cisco 3650/3850 Switch from 3.x to 16.1.1 Frist, grab the software here: IOS XE Denali 16.1.1 on Cisco.
